Package: folder-zipper-versioning
Version: 1.2
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-tk
Maintainer: codingismynewgaming
Description: Folder Zipper with automatic versioning
 A Python Tkinter GUI application that zips folders with automatic
 version numbering and custom version support.
 .
 Features:
 - Easy folder selection via GUI
 - Auto version numbering (001, 002, 003...)
 - Custom version input field
 - Timestamp in filenames
 - Dark mode support
 - Directory navigation
 - Donation links and GitHub issue reporting
Homepage: https://github.com/codingismynewgaming/folder-zip-versioning
